"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1930086-Andy-Murray-Dan-Evans-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murrayis refusing to go away despite announcing that the Olympics will be the final tournament of his career.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The former world No.\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1's retirement will have to wait, as he is through to the quarter-final of the men's doubles event withDan Evans.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After theyproduced a heroic comeback in the first round- saving five consecutive match points - the British duo were back at it against Belgium's Sander Gille and Joran Vliegen.\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9994640647463998, \"rank\": 0.0005318209216339792, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.929797060450397, \"rank\": 0.07500667035369799, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joran Vliegen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a much faster start than their last match as they broke immediately but it turned into a dramatic battle as Murray and Evans blew two match points in the second set tiebreak before saving two in the match tiebreak.\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they ultimately went on to win 6-3 6-7(8) 11-9.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evans stepped up to serve first and the British duo were in a tricky spot as they were forced to save two break points.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9994640647463998, \"rank\": 0.0005318209216339792, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they responded perfectly, holding on before taking a 0-40 lead on Vliegen's serve.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evans broke at the second time of asking with a lob winner his partner would be proud of and roared.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Murray had to prove that he was the king of lobs, making a winner of his own to extend their lead to 3-0.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stands in Court Suzanne Lenglen were half empty, just like Sunday night, as the spectators took a break after witnessingRafael NadalandCarlos Alcarazwin their own doubles match.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Suzanne Lenglen\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there were plenty of Union Jacks in the crowd - after Murray and Evans' heroics in the last round, the fans had reason to believe.\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1334, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999936983561668, \"rank\": 6.301573973195178e-06, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheers from Court 7 drowned out the noise in Lenglen as French duo Caroline Garcia and Dianne Parry competed their own Murray-style comeback in their first set of their women's doubles match, going from 2-5 to 7-5.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9794194774551073, \"rank\": 0.020373250512092034, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Garcia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Garcia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Garcia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Olympics tennis star tells opponent 'I do not respect you' in heated row  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  The British fans still made themselves heard and spurred on their men as Evans found himself in a tricky spot serving for the set.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9994640647463998, \"rank\": 0.0005318209216339792, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He received a time violation at 30-30 and threw his racket in frustration when a return winner gave the Belgians a break point.\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray screamed \\\"let us go\\\" as they saved it and they finally took the set 6-3 after 43 minutes.\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second set was a lot closer but there was a sense that things could be shifting as Gille served at 3-3.\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From 40-0 up, the Belgians suddenly found themselves at 40-30 as Evans ripped a forehand winner straight past the pair.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2430, \"end\": 2435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gille kept them ahead but there was something in the air.\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As songs of \\\"allez les blues\\\" carried over from Court 7 again, Murray and Evans gave the Lenglen crowd a reason to shut them out as they earned the first break point of the set.\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2606, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2617, \"end\": 2622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The noise was quickly replaced with chants of \\\"let us go, GB\\\".\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2780, \"end\": 2782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.5882659994370327, \"rank\": 0.6880031906083259, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Vliegen came up clutch and held them off.\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brits had to serve to stay in the set again.\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2831, \"end\": 2840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Brits\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, Murray was tasked with the job.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2891, \"end\": 2897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He fired down an ace before they forced a tiebreak.\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Rafael Nadal doubts shut down as Carlos Alcaraz 'forced to make special request'  Do not miss:Tennis star issues cryptic statement after withdrawing from Olympics event  Do not miss:Gauff explains why she got so upset with umpire during shock defeat at Olympics  It was a rollercoaster - neither team could hold on to any mini-break leads.\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 3327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2988, \"end\": 3000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brits had a match point at 6-4 but Vliegen saved it with a winner.\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3328, \"end\": 3337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Brits\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Murray's turn to save a set point before they had another chance to close it out.\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3406, \"end\": 3412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was saved by another winner and, facing another set point, Evans gave it away with a double fault.\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3550, \"end\": 3555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the second match in a row, Murray's career hinged on a first-to-10-point match tiebreak.\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3622, \"end\": 3628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, it was filled with mini-breaks.\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There seemed to be no clear winner emerging in the tense, winner-take-all breaker.\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gille and Vliegen were edging towards the finish line as they gave themselves two match points.\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the second, as Gille served for it, Murray came up with a huge return and an error kept his career alive.\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 4011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3942, \"end\": 3948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All of a sudden, they had their third match point.\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fittingly, it was the former world No.\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 who stepped up to serve to continue his career.\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And for the second match in a row, he produced a miracle escape to push off his retirement.\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray and Evans have made it no secret that they want to do something special for the former No.\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4245, \"end\": 4251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.898376034284604e-50, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 4256, \"end\": 4261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.449192981637368e-10, \"t